,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:02:52.000Z","msg":"我睇左少少網上講 懷疑自己係神經性腳臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n響屋企赤腳冇味 但係一著鞋（就算係透氣果d波鞋）就臭 <br />\n跟住搭車又覺得人地聞到我腳臭 響度細聲講大聲笑<br />\n跟住又越緊張 就越臭 臭到自己都聞到 但係唔係up味 係d唔知咩味"},{"pid":"76c41d3cad5738a68b706120779ec2028a9dccf7","tid":1393984,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:06:09.000Z","msg":"食清d 做運動出汗 著清爽鞋"},{"pid":"933af629f77725db144ea937e1573d41f543982f","tid":1393984,"uid":261448,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:11:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.gamme.com.tw/1641843\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gamme.com.tw%2F1641843&d=H0od%2FlU2Kx31F%2BxGtrrl509C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=62101e88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.gamme.com.tw/1641843</a><br />\n<br />\nYou are not alone.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2019/18/43/qZqWoqOel6SWrqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2019%2F18%2F43%2FqZqWoqOel6SWrqQ.jpg&h=bcc1629a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e3f9b26ffbaacab65b2e6f6cc1da655d93f7cfe","tid":1393984,"uid":25559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76c41d3cad5738a68b706120779ec2028a9dccf7","tid":1393984,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:06:09.000Z","msg":"食清d 做運動出汗 著清爽鞋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:24:05.000Z","msg":"自從發覺有味之後已經請左大假 以為香港腳 <br />\n響屋企日日搽藥浸藥水 以為冇事啦 <br />\n換哂新腳襪 點知一搭車就臭 覺得隔離d人聞到我腳臭 個人就越緊張越臭 <br />\n<br />\n如果你依排搭車隔離條友隻腳好臭 對唔住啊 我都唔想 上網睇話冇得醫 係神經病變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c90c21d07432fa8533900739bb49522044d6ed2","tid":1393984,"uid":112709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:29:32.000Z","msg":"比班狗聞"},{"pid":"a382dc0bfdda128bdb9cdee74b6ed098f4ebe2c8","tid":1393984,"uid":25559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot